        dc:description           "FIGURES 99–110. Hypatropis sternalis (Stål, 1869). 99–100: Habitus dorsal and ventral. 101–102: Head, dorsal and lateral view; 103–105: Pygophore in dorsal, posterior and ventral view; 106–108: Phallus in dorsal, lateral, ventral and posterolateral view; 109: Genital plates in posteroventral view; 110: Female receptaculum seminis and aussenwand. Abbreviations: ddr, distal ductus receptaculi; pdr, proximal ductus receptaculi; va, vesicular area. Scale bars = 99–100: 1.0 mm; 101–102, 109–110: 0.5 mm; 103–105: 1.0 mm; 106–108: 0.25 mm." ;
